≥GIVEN IN LOVING MEMORY OF
TOM HILLIER
A DEVOTED HUSBAND AND
FOR MANY YEARS A CHORISTER AND
PAROCHIAL CHURCH COUNCILLOR OF
St. MARY'S CHURCH, BATHWICK
DIED 18th.FEBRUARY 1969"π
∂Harold Swindells 
Co-founder of Bath Postal Museum
He enjoyed walking in this park 
and liked to stop and look at every tree. 
